					<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><h2> <span class="mw-headline" id="Definition">Definition</span></h2>
<p>A locus is the specific physical location of a gene or other DNA sequence on a chromosome. The term is occasionally (albeit imprecisely) used synonymously with "gene". Plural of locus is loci.</p>
